      <format type="text/markdown"><![CDATA[  
  
## Remarks  
 The SocketOptionLevel enumeration defines the socket option levels that can be passed to the <xref:System.Net.Sockets.Socket.SetSocketOption%2A?displayProperty=fullName> and <xref:System.Net.Sockets.Socket.GetSocketOption%2A?displayProperty=fullName> methods. <xref:System.Net.Sockets.SocketOptionName> enumerated values are grouped by SocketOptionLevel.  
  
 **Note** To use IPv6 on Windows XP, install Advance Networking Pack for Windows XP.  
  
   
  
